Missing source metadata is a search-admission error.

## 7.4 Candidate priority and eviction

Protected candidates:

```text
terminal_exact_v1
opponent exact cover pairs
impossible-to-cover diagnostic pairs
```

must not be evicted by ordinary budget pressure.

Eviction order for non-protected candidates:

```text
1. duplicates
2. illegal or stale hash rows
3. low-score excess from overfilled source quota
4. low-diversity redundant candidates
5. lowest final candidate priority
```

Blind canaries:

```text
may be searched if configured as real legal candidates
must be training_forbidden unless explicitly promoted
must be separately counted
```

